            "title": "觀塘綠景NEO全幢甲廈淪銀主盤 內房9年前90億天價買入 估值料大幅腰斬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"573\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZHvs5UZ5PVGoWu2_Syg14Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/28hse_com_210/5ca47d017e7ae665493f5c5526d54e28\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
